U.S. Monetization of Debt Makes Yen Attractive, Lord Abbett’s Ezrati Says

-- B y   D a v e   L i e d t k a
-- 
2011-06-07T15:01:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-07/u-s-monetization-of-debt-makes-yen-attractive-lord-abbett-s-ezrati-says.html
U.S. policies that equate to the
monetization of the nation’s debt makes the yen attractive
versus the dollar, according to Milton Ezrati, senior economic
strategist at Lord Abbett & Co.   Ezrati, who made the comments during Bloomberg Link’s Japan
Conference in  New York , also said  Europe ’s debt crisis makes the
yen attractive versus the euro.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dave Liedtka at 
 dliedtka@bloomberg.net  